Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.maps.DefaultMetaDataHolder
      • com.atakmap.android.maps.MapData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetaDataHolder

    public class MapData
extends DefaultMetaDataHolder
    Stub class to help transition away from the use of a Bundle as a backer for the MapView::getMapData class. See bugs: ATAK-8435, ATAK-8745
